cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and sentiment analysis. The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the use of transfer learning could place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the focus on sentiment analysis could also suggest that it belongs to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
